-- ============================================================================
-- demo-store-seed.sql — 50-product fashion store (Myntra subset, hand-curated)
-- Fully ENRICHED (samesake 2-stage gate pipeline) + INDEXED (gemini-embedding-2).
-- Reproduces the search-credibility / quarantine demo with ZERO LLM calls.
--
-- 40 ready + 10 quarantined (non-apparel / low-confidence / cross-signal-disagree).
--
-- Usage:
--   1. Bootstrap samesake system tables once (run the app, or matcher.migrate()).
--   2. psql "$DATABASE_URL" -f examples/fashion-search/datasets/demo-store-seed.sql
--   Then: matcher.search("demo_store", "products", { q: "navy blue shirt for men" })
--
-- Regenerate after any collection-schema change: see seed-demo-store.ts.
-- ============================================================================
